headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Receives Second Request for Information Related to its HSR Filing for the Purchase of AssuredPartners
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. ("Gallagher") today announced it has received a request for additional information as part of the Hart-Scott-Rodino ("HSR") filing related to its proposed acquisition of AssuredPartners, Inc. A second request for information is a common feature of the regulatory review for transactions of this type.
